<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-9">
        <h1>Forum Methods</h1>
        <p>All the below methods deal with reading and writing data related to the forum.</p>


        <h2>Methods to Get Information</h2>

        <h3>Reading the board List</h3>
        <dl>
            <dt>URI Format</dt><dd>forum</dd>
            <dt>Method</dt><dd>GET</dd>
            <dt>Authentication</dt><dd>No</dd>
        </dl>
        <p>Retrieves the list of all the forum boards. Output is an <a href="{{ path('_docs_responses') }}#forum">forum list</a>.</p>

        <h3>Reading the topic List</h3>
        <dl>
            <dt>URI Format</dt><dd>forum/<em>id</em></dd>
            <dt>Method</dt><dd>GET</dd>
            <dt>Authentication</dt><dd>No</dd>
        </dl>
        <p>Retrieves the topic list of the specified by the id number. Output is an <a href="{{ path('_docs_responses') }}#forum">forum list</a>.</p>
        <p>The values that can be sent in the post body:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>page</code>:  The current set of topics to return. Each set contains at most 20 items. Default value is &quot;1&quot; if not supplied.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Reading the topic Details</h3>
        <dl>
            <dt>URI Format</dt><dd>forum/topic/<em>id</em></dd>
            <dt>Method</dt><dd>GET</dd>
            <dt>Authentication</dt><dd>No</dd>
        </dl>
        <p>Retrieves the topic details (like comments) of the specified by the id number. Output is an <a href="{{ path('_docs_responses') }}#forum">forum list</a>.</p>
        <p>The values that can be sent in the post body:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>page</code>:  The current set of topic details to return. Each set contains at most 20 items. Default value is &quot;1&quot; if not supplied.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Methods to Change Information</h2>

        <p class="alert alert-info">All post data <strong>must</strong> be sent as x-www-form-urlencoded as the API does not currently support multipart/form-data!</p>

        <h3>Adding Topics</h3>
        <dl>
            <dt>URI Format</dt><dd>forum/<em>id</em></dd>
            <dt>Method</dt><dd>POST</dd>
            <dt>Authentication</dt><dd>Required</dd>
        </dl>
        <p>Adds an topic to the specified board.</p>
        <p>The values that can be sent in the post body:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>title</code>: The title for the topic</li>
            <li><code>message</code>: The message for the topic.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Add Comments</h3>
        <dl>
            <dt>URI Format</dt><dd>forum/topic/<em>id</em></dd>
            <dt>Method</dt><dd>POST</dd>
            <dt>Authentication</dt><dd>Required</dd>
        </dl>
        <p>Adds a comment to the specified topic.</p>
        <p>The values that can be sent in the post body:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>message</code>: The comment for the topic.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Edit Comments</h3>
        <dl>
            <dt>URI Format</dt><dd>forum/topic/<em>id</em></dd>
            <dt>Method</dt><dd>PUT</dd>
            <dt>Authentication</dt><dd>Required</dd>
        </dl>
        <p>Edits a comment of the specified topic.</p>
        <p>The values that can be sent in the post body:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>message</code>: The modified comment for the topic.</li>
        </ul>

        <hr>
    </div>
</div>

